ینال سابقه بازیگری در آثاری همچون رقص با گرگ ها، گریزلی ها، استامپ تاون، تاریکی را حفظ کن و افسانه خزان را در کارنامه هنری خود دارد.","name":"تانتو کاردینال","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"タントゥー・カーディナル","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"טנטו קרדינל","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Танту Кардинал","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"تانتو كاردينال","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Τάντου Κάρντιναλ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"丹圖·卡蒂娜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Tantoo Cardinal CM 加拿大女演员。在50年的时间里，她获得了130多个学分，获得了无数奖项，包括厄尔·格雷奖，2009年，她被授予加拿大勋章，“以表彰她对加拿大原住民表演艺术的成长和发展的贡献，作为银幕和舞台女演员，以及萨斯喀彻温省原住民剧院公司的创始成员。她出演了斯科塞斯的《花月杀手》，她即将上映的项目包括漫威系列《回声》和动画长片《温德尔与怀尔德》。她以在 Stumptown 和 3 Pines 的工作而闻名，在《堕落传奇》、《与狼共舞》和《风河》等电影以及《SEE》、《西部世界》和《边境》等电视节目中有着丰富的历史。Tantoo Cardinal 拥有多个荣誉博士学位。","name":"坦图·卡丁诺","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"丹圖·卡蒂娜 CM 加拿大女演員。在 50 年的時間裏，她獲得了 130 多個學分，獲得了無數獎項，包括厄爾·格雷獎，2009 年，她被授豫加拿大勳章，“以表彰她對加拿大原住民表演藝術的成長和發展的貢獻，作為銀幕和舞台女演員，以及薩斯喀徹温省原住民劇院公司的創始成員。她出演了斯科塞斯的《花月殺手》，她即將上映的項目包括漫威系列《命運迴音谷》和動畫長片《温德爾與懷爾德》。她以在 Stumptown 和 3 Pines 的工作而聞名，在《墮落傳奇》、《與狼共舞》和《風河》等電影以及《SEE》、《西部世界》和《邊境奇聞》等電視節目中有著豐富的歷史。丹圖·卡蒂娜 擁有多個榮譽博士學位。","name":"丹圖·卡蒂娜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Танту Кардінал","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"ca","name":"Català","english_name":"Catalan","data":{"biography":"Tantoo Caroline Rose Cardinal CM (Anzac, Canadà, 20 de juliol de 1950) és una actriu canadenca d'herència Cree i Métis. El 2009 va ser nomenada membre de l'Ordre del Canadà \"per les seves contribucions al creixement i desenvolupament de les arts.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_1184640_translations":{"at":1774211380035,"data":{"id":1184640,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Paulo Gorgulho é um ator brasileiro.\n\nFicou conhecido por atuar na novela Pantanal e no filme O Cangaceiro, ambos na década de 90, além de ter interpretado Anrão, pai de Moisés na novela Os Dez Mandamentos em 2015.","name":"Paulo Gorgulho","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Paulo César Gorgulho, better known as Paulo Gorgulho, is a Brazilian actor, known for having starred in the telenovela Pantanal and the film O Cangaceiro. In 2005, he gained prominence as the main antagonist of Estes Mulheres, a telenovela based on the work of José de Alencar.","name":"Paulo Gorgulho","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"保罗·戈尔古略","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"保羅·戈爾古略","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1311850_credits":{"at":1774211389376,"data":{"id":1311850,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":106725,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kathryn Davis","original_name":"Kathryn Davis","popularity":1.1274,"profile_path":"/hs3fjziV9U4cmw4Px92KRbfE1Ea.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Felicity","credit_id":"668452a471ac33f2e517a59a","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1460686,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Jack Murray","original_name":"J